data.description: Nestled in a peaceful suburban neighborhood, this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a harmonious blend of comfort and functionality. Inside, an open-concept living area connects the living room, dining space, and modern kitchen, creating an ideal setting for daily life and entertaining. Tiled floors and ample windows accentuate the space with natural light. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and a breakfast bar.The owner's bedroom features an en-suite bathroom and 2 generous walk-in  closets. As well as three other versatile bedrooms await, adaptable to various needs. The backyard offers a serene escape with a patio for outdoor gatherings.Modern amenities include a laundry room and energy-efficient systems. Conveniently located near schools, shopping, and easy transportation access, this home encapsulates comfort and convenience for families seeking a tranquil yet well-connected lifestyle.
